title: Bobby's Fancy Mini-Van Dinner + Eddie vs. Lunchbox: Fun Fact Friday! + Bobby’s Mailbag: Woman Wants To Track Her Husband
itunes:title: Bobby's Fancy Mini-Van Dinner + Eddie vs. Lunchbox: Fun Fact Friday! + Bobby’s Mailbag: Woman Wants To Track Her Husband
description:
Bobby talks about going to Nobu in Malibu, CA which is famous for celebrities sightings which is why paparazzi are waiting outside. However, Bobby talks about how he pulled up in a mini-van. Eddie and Lunchbox go another round batting in Fun Facts they found on the internet. Bobby reads an email from a listener who wants to track her husband on his iPhone…but he’s not having it.
